I was just sitting here trying to think of a title for a new thread..and from out of no where this came to me!<br><br>
It doesn't matter what the title is.. we seem to drift anyway into a fight or silliness.  Although, some titles have been appropriate in the past.<br><br>
There has been a lot of good solid poop posted lately, thanks to the fillasockfull smart persons.  That is needed!<br>
Some sadness has rocked the boat.. well, that's good too, in a way.<br><br>
Spatz continues to bounce off the wall of his pen of paranoia, blurting drugged excuses for hidden regrets.<br><br>
Tangents are taken with great fecundity to avoid direct confrontation with private fears.  Denial is facilitated by shifting focus.  I am always more healthy when rescuing or criticising others or lapsing into questionable humor.<br><br>
In spite of all the subliminal squirming.. I have learned something through osmosis.  Perhaps it is time for me to introspect and air out some suppressed/repressed garbage without deviating to focus on others...finding fault with institutions and individuals.. making excuses for my wounds.<br>
Ever so briefly that emerges.. but is quickly swept back under the carpet.<br><br>
It is good to have brothers around you when you fall flat on your ass.  It is easy to see pain in our brothers and offer good advice... eventually, we may be able to see our own pain and heed our own advice.<br><br>
It's a long road!
